I am afraid of you?

1255
01:37:21,306 --> 01:37:23,306
Cos otherwise she would
be dead already.

1256
01:37:23,306 --> 01:37:25,426
You need a bargaining chip.

1257
01:37:30,986 --> 01:37:33,546
Stop there! Hands up!

1258
01:37:33,546 --> 01:37:36,226
If you kill me
you'll never get it open.

1259
01:37:38,666 --> 01:37:40,506
Move away. Move!

1260
01:37:47,346 --> 01:37:51,266
You know John, I feel like
we have gotten off on the wrong foot.

1261
01:37:51,946 --> 01:37:55,266
And 'cos of that you think
I'm the bad guy,

1262
01:37:55,306 --> 01:37:58,306
