1292
01:39:37,226 --> 01:39:39,426
- It's brilliant.
- Yes, it is.

1293
01:39:39,426 --> 01:39:41,906
- Please, be quiet.
- Asshole.

1294
01:39:41,906 --> 01:39:44,906
