- Matt Farrell.

1295
01:39:45,786 --> 01:39:47,146
Lucy McClane.

1296
01:39:47,826 --> 01:39:50,146
I thought your name was Gennero.

1297
01:39:50,226 --> 01:39:51,706
Lucy Gennero?

1298
01:39:51,746 --> 01:39:54,826
- Not today.
- Can you crack the code?

1299
01:39:55,066 --> 01:39:57,386
Maybe, if I had enough time.

1300
01:39:57,626 --> 01:39:58,946
That is encouraging.

1301
01:40:00,866 --> 01:40:02,066
We take them with us.

1302
01:40:02,946 --> 01:40:05,466
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

1303
01:40:07,626 --> 01:40:10,506
