1323
01:43:48,706 --> 01:43:51,066
Robertson is coming too fast.

1324
01:43:54,666 --> 01:43:55,986
It's not Robertson.

1325
01:43:56,586 --> 01:43:58,506
That would be my Dad.

1326
01:44:09,466 --> 01:44:10,506
Freddy!

1327
01:44:12,426 --> 01:44:13,546
Freddy!

1328
01:44:15,426 --> 01:44:17,866
This is John McClane.
Look I know you can hear me.

1329
01:44:17,866 --> 01:44:19,506
This is your frequency, right?

1330
01:44:19,506 --> 01:44:22,186
666. Come on pick
up the mic, Freddy.

1331
01:44:25,306 --> 01:44:27,906
Nobody here by that name, sorry.

1332
01:44:27,906 --> 01:44:29,906
Hacker jerk off!

1333
01:44:34,226 --> 01:44:35,666
Warlock!

1334
01:44:36,146 --> 01:44:39,066
I need you to do whatever
it is that you do...

1335
01:44:39,066 --> 01:44:41,066
to patch me through
to the F.B.I.

1336
01:44:41,066 --> 01:44:44,186
To Deputy Director Bowman,
you hear me?

1337
01:44:44,466 --> 01:44:47,826
Are you serious, you want me
to intentionally open up a com...

1338
01:44:47,826 --> 01:44:52,186
line to the head of the C.I.A.
cyber division? I don't think so.

1339
01:44:52,186 --> 01:44:55,466
