reach you.

1344
01:45:18,546 --> 01:45:19,786
Go.

1345
01:45:19,866 --> 01:45:21,986
- Bowman, it's McClane.
- McClane.

1346
01:45:21,986 --> 01:45:24,466
Listen to me,
Gabriel is on the 695,

1347
01:45:24,466 --> 01:45:26,066
headed north, in a
haz-mat truck.

1348
01:45:26,066 --> 01:45:29,066
Wait, Gabriel has left Woodlawn?
We were heading there right now.

1349
01:45:29,066 --> 01:45:32,066
Bowman, he's got my daughter.

1350
01:45:33,266 --> 01:45:37,946
Listen, this haz-mat truck, it's a
government vehicle so it is tracked, right?

1351
01:45:37,946 --> 01:45:40,346
Track that down,
should take you right to him.

1352
01:45:40,346 --> 01:45:42,266
- Gimmie the tag number?
- Alright,

1353
01:45:42,266 --> 01:45:43,866
Here it comes.

1354
01:45:43,906 --> 01:45:46,626
Golf, Tango...

1355
01:45:47,106 --> 01:45:50,506
592, November.

1356
01:45:50,986 --> 01:45:53,866
Got it.
McClane, where is Farrell?

1357
01:45:53,866 --> 01:45:55,306
He is with them.

1358
01:45:56,746 --> 01:45:59,946
Listen to me, I'm gonna
go in there and get Lucy out.

1359
01:46:00,626 --> 01:46:02,546
But if something happens to me...

1360
01:46:02,546 --> 01:46:04,586
you gotta send in the cavalry,
do you hear me?

1361
01:46:04,586 --> 01:46:08,746
I mean everybody, don't let that
maniac get my daughter, you hear me?

1362
01:46:08,746 --> 01:46:10,266
John, don't worry.

1363
01:46:10,266 --> 01:46:12,506
I want your word, Bowman.

1364
01:46:14,146 --> 01:46:15,546
Yeah, you have it.

1365
01:46:16,746 --> 01:46:18,306
Why not?

1366
01:46:24,946 --> 01:46:26,666
There's the F-35.

1367
01:46:29,106 --> 01:46:31,026
Did you get the go codes?

1368
01:46:31,026 --> 01:46:33,946
- Trey! Did you get the go codes?
- Yes, I got the go codes.

1369
01:46:33,946 --> 01:46:36,146
Can you connect me to the pilot?

1370
01:46:52,106 --> 01:46:54,226
