01:47:09,626 --> 01:47:12,946
AV-81, this is Marine Airway. ATC.

1374
01:47:13,026 --> 01:47:14,426
Gofer, AV-81.

1375
01:47:14,426 --> 01:47:18,626
Confirmed terrorist vehicle has been
located in your sector. Big-Rig Truck.

1376
01:47:19,306 --> 01:47:22,186
- We are in pursuit of a Haz-mat vehicle.
- I'm hearing you, ATC.

1377
01:47:22,186 --> 01:47:24,906
You are authorised to engage and destroy.

1378
01:47:25,106 --> 01:47:27,226
Copy that,
AV-81 engaging.

1379
01:47:35,706 --> 01:47:36,946
What...

1380
01:47:46,066 --> 01:47:47,466
God damn it!

1381
01:47:50,186 --> 01:47:52,226
You're shooting the wrong guy!

1382
01:47:59,386 --> 01:48:01,866
I don't think Daddy's
coming, honey.

1383
01:48:13,106 --> 01:48:16,546
Hey! Jackass!

1384
01:49:01,586 --> 01:49:03,146
Is that it?

1385
01:49:06,506 --> 01:49:08,386
