1386
01:51:47,706 --> 01:51:50,426
Come on, get out. That way.

1387
01:52:00,026 --> 01:52:02,946
We are leaving in 3 minutes.

1388
01:52:05,546 --> 01:52:07,906
You have 1.

1389
01:52:07,946 --> 01:52:12,546
The rules didn't change man, you're
gonna kill me as soon as I unlock it.

1390
01:52:15,666 --> 01:52:17,586
- Ah, shit!
- Matthew?

1391
01:52:17,586 --> 01:52:21,186
Matthew! I really need
you to pay attention.

1392
01:52:21,866 --> 01:52:24,346
The rules can always change.

1393
01:52:24,346 --> 01:52:27,066
- OK OK.
- I will shoot in her in 10 seconds.

1394
01:52:27,066 --> 01:52:29,986
- Wait, wait.
- Nine.

1395
01:52:30,146 --> 01:52:32,346
- I can't...
- Eight.

1396
01:52:33,066 --> 01:52:34,666
I can't...

1397
01:52:35,706 --> 01:52:37,026
Oh, God!

1398
01:52:39,826 --> 01:52:42,226
OK!

1399
01:52:42,706 --> 01:52:44,426
OK OK OK!

1400
01:52:44,626 --> 01:52:46,066
Six.

1401
01:52:46,226 --> 01:52:48,986
OK, stop stop,
I'm doing it.

1402
01:52:48,986 --> 01:52:50,786
I'm doing it. Oh, God!

1403
01:53:05,386 --> 01:53:07,746
The Feds are heading this way.

1404
01:53:07,826 --> 01:53:10,026
Get everything on the plane.

1405
01:53:17,946 --> 01:53:19,706
- Dad?
- Careful.

1406
01:53:20,386 --> 01:53:24,706
Don't worry baby,
Everything is going to be alright.

1407
01:53:26,226 --> 01:53:27,706
Daddy!

1408
01:53:34,906 --> 01:53:36,306
Hold this.

1409
01:54:01,306 --> 01:54:02,946
Jesus Christ!

1410
01:54:03,386 --> 01:54:05,226
You got her?

1411
01:54:05,746 --> 01:54:07,186
You sure?

1412
01:54:09,626 --> 01:54:11,546
Nice effort though.

1413
01:54:11,546 --> 01:54:12,986
Matthew?

1414
01:54:13,466 --> 01:54:15,426
Shit. OK.

1415
01:54:15,426 --> 01:54:17,146
I'm doing it,
I know.

1416
01:54:24,106 --> 01:54:25,546
McClane...

1417
01:54:26,426 --> 01:54:28,266
Would you do me
a favour?

1418
01:54:30,386 --> 01:54:32,786
I know the lights are
beginning to dim...

1419
01:54:32,786 --> 01:54:35,186
but if you can just hang
on for a second...

1420
01:54:35,186 --> 01:54:38,586
as soon as Matts finishes,
I'm gonna kill him and your daughter

1421
01:54:38,586 --> 01:54:41,586
