to see that.

1422
01:54:42,786 --> 01:54:44,586
God damn it. Mathew?

1423
01:54:44,786 --> 01:54:47,786
10 second,  OK 10 seconds
and you will have all your money.

1424
01:54:47,786 --> 01:54:49,626
You can just leave, nobody
has to get hurt, OK?

1425
01:54:49,626 --> 01:54:52,586
A few seconds. Stay
with me, McClane...

1426
01:54:54,026 --> 01:54:57,146
- Stay with me.
- Dad?

1427
01:54:57,546 --> 01:54:59,786
On your tombstone
it shall read:

1428
01:54:59,826 --> 01:55:02,906
"Always in the wrong place, at the wrong time"

1429
01:55:03,706 --> 01:55:07,626
How about:
"Yippi-kai-ay, mother fu..."

1430
01:55:20,966 --> 01:55:22,206
Daddy?

1431
01:55:22,726 --> 01:55:25,246
- Are you OK?
- Yeah, I'm fine...

1432
01:55:27,326 --> 01:55:29,726
I knew you would come for me.

1433
01:55:29,766 --> 01:55:33,446
