It's OK.

1434
01:55:47,606 --> 01:55:48,846
Freeze!

1435
01:55:49,526 --> 01:55:52,246
Hold up, Hold up!
He's OK.

1436
01:55:57,806 --> 01:56:00,006
Help Daddy up.

1437
01:56:01,246 --> 01:56:03,206
I think I'll just stay
here for a minute.

1438
