1443
01:56:33,846 --> 01:56:37,886
Lift your arms up,
Now put them down, further.

1444
01:56:38,766 --> 01:56:41,646
He might die from shock
on the way to the hospital.

1445
01:56:45,526 --> 01:56:46,966
Alright.

1446
01:56:49,406 --> 01:56:50,806
I'll be right back.

1447
01:56:53,246 --> 01:56:56,166
- Hey.
