1462
01:57:51,206 --> 01:57:53,886
What was I gonna do?

1463
01:57:55,046 --> 01:57:57,446
That's what makes
you "that" guy.

1464
01:57:59,886 --> 01:58:01,286
Yeah.

1465
01:58:08,216 --> 01:58:10,336
